See’s Candies Raised Prices by 2.5% in January, WSJ Reports

-- B y   C l a u d i a   C a r p e n t e r
-- 
2011-02-18T06:27:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/see-s-candies-raised-prices-by-2-5-in-january-wsj-reports.html
See’s Candies raised prices by 2.5
percent in January after higher costs for chocolate and sugar,
the Wall Street Journal said, citing an unidentified
spokeswoman. 
  The price changes are considered “short-term issues,” the
spokeswoman said, according to the Journal.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
